WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:31.060
Europe has 12 constellations, while China has 12 animals symbolising

00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:34.500
the 12 branches used to designate years.

00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:45.720
The 12 animals finish a cycle every 12 years and each
of them guards one year.

00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:55.980
Chinese believe that those who are born in a certain year

00:00:56.180 --> 00:00:59.700
would inherit the traits of the animal guarding that year.

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:11.520
Rats are wise

00:01:16.180 --> 00:01:18.300
and cattle are hard-working.

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:24.120
Tigers are courageous

00:01:25.580 --> 00:01:27.580
and rabbits are prudent.

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:33.960
Dragons are rich and respectful,

00:01:34.940 --> 00:01:36.760
and snakes are romantic.

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:39.320
Horses are fast

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:42.600
and a sheep are sincere.

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:47.720
Monkeys are smart and flexible,

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:52.420
while chickens are endowed with beauty.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:57.740
Dogs are faithful and pigs are amiable.

00:02:04.360 --> 00:02:08.720
Do you know what your symbolic animal
denoting the year of your birth?

